sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The external interfaces of KRM are described by the Component Diagram "Interfaces" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.KRM_Chorus.SW Architecture.Static
A part of the external interfaces used by KRM is provided by the component "RTE Light QM" and includes generated interfaces: SST_KRM: "sw.sys.chorus_main_doc\mc_sw\cdd\ECU_DIAG_Chorus\KRM\c\cfg\sst\KRM_Sst.xlsx" see also Component Diagram "SW Architecture" at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.KRM_Chorus.SW Architecture

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The module has dependencies to the following modules.

The external dependencies of KRM are described by the Component Diagram "Dependencies" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.KRM_Chorus.SW Architecture.Static
